OL,4,CShein: China fashion giant investigates
OL,5,C'false' anti-Uyghur job ads
OL,6, Chinese fast fashion firm Shein has
OL,7, launched an investigation into "false"
OL,8, discriminatory job adverts posted on
OL,9, recruitment sites under its name.
OL,11,FAdverts seen by the BBC for factory and
OL,12,Fwarehouse workers said those from
OL,13,Fcertain ethnic minority backgrounds,
OL,14,Fincluding Uyghurs, must not apply.
OL,16,FShein said it did not fund or approve
OL,17,Fthe ads, and it was committed to
OL,18,F"upholding high labour standards".
OL,20,FThe plight of the Uyghurs in China has
OL,21,Fsparked international condemnation.
